┤VERA & STAN GRAHAM
B 1907  D 1991/7
EACH IS GIVEN A BAG OF TOOLS
A SHAPELESS MASS, A BOOK OF RULES
AND EACH MUST MAKE ERE LIFE IS FLOWN
A STUMBLING-BLOCK OR A. STEPPING-STONE."╗
ĖSimon John Kwiecinski
01.09.1973 - 06.10.2013
(Dada, Kwif. Special K, Ski, K-Dog)
Remembering you is easy, we do it every day
It's just the pain of losing you, that never goes away"Š
╗Mary Zammit
2nd May 1923 - 26th November 2014
Your life was a blessing your memory treasured every day
An amazing Mum, Nan & Great Grandma
Peter Paul Zammit
7th May 1922 - 10th May 2012
A wonderful dad, grandad & great grandad. In memory of all
the happy times spent here in this park with your grandchildren"┐
